PN,37701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FValdo Calocane "lied, deceived and
OL,8,Foutmanoeuvred" medical staff before he
OL,9,Fwent on to kill three people and
OL,10,Fattempt to kill three more, a mental
OL,11,Fhealth nurse has told The Nottingham
OL,12,FInquiry.
OL,14,FGary Carter, who was part of the Early
OL,15,FIntervention in Psychosis (EIP) team
OL,16,Fand was Calocane's care co-ordinator
OL,17,Fbetween April and September 2022, said
OL,18,F"95%" of what he knows about the
OL,19,FNottingham killer he has learned since
OL,20,Fthe fatal attacks in June 2023.
OL,26,@oD@POUpD@NO]zD@AOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FParanoid schizophrenic Calocane was
OL,8,Fsentenced to an indefinite hospital
OL,9,Forder in January 2024 after fatally
OL,10,Fstabbing students Barnaby Webber and
OL,11,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar, 19, as well as
OL,12,Fschool caretaker Ian Coates, 65, in a
OL,13,Fviolent rampage across the city.
OL,15,FHe went on to seriously injure Wayne
OL,16,FBirkett, Sharon Miller and Marcin
OL,17,FGawronski.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FGiving evidence at the central London
OL,8,Fhearing on Thursday, Mr Carter, who
OL,9,Fresigned from Nottinghamshire
OL,10,FHealthcare NHS Foundation Trust in
OL,11,FApril 2025, was asked by counsel to
OL,12,Fthe inquiry Rachel Langdale KC what
OL,13,Fwent wrong with Calocane's care in the
OL,14,Fcommunity.
OL,16,FHe said: "Most of what I know about
OL,17,FVC, I would say 95%, I would say I
OL,18,Fhave learned since this sad tragedy in
OL,19,FJune 2023.
OL,26,@xD@JOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"Basically, I think this man, in a
OL,8,Fnutshell, he lied, he deceived, he
OL,9,Foutmanoeuvred the medical staff on the
OL,10,Fward and in the community.
OL,12,F"He wasn't honest... he is saying all
OL,13,Fthe right words and I don't think
OL,14,Fpeople fully appreciated that at the
OL,15,Ftime.
OL,17,F"I think it is very easy to see this
OL,18,Fnow but at the time, without the
OL,19,Fbenefit of hindsight, he outmanoeuvred
OL,20,Fmedical and nursing services."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMr Carter said he felt he had done "as
OL,8,Fmuch as I possibly could" when he was
OL,9,FCalocane's care co-ordinator and saw
OL,10,Fhim twice during that period, but
OL,11,Fadmitted he had not fully read his
OL,12,Frecords.
OL,14,FHe also admitted he had not seen a
OL,15,Fnote dated 16 July 2020 from
OL,16,Fconsultant psychiatrist Dr Faizal
OL,17,FSeedat, who treated the killer at
OL,18,FHighbury Hospital in Nottinghamshire,
OL,19,Fin which he said Calocane had "no
OL,20,Finsight or remorse" and would perhaps
OL,21,Fend up killing someone.
OL,26,@oD@dOUpD@YO]{D@_OU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FHe also did not know about previous
OL,8,Fviolent incidents that Calocane had
OL,9,Fbeen involved in, including one in
OL,10,Fwhich a woman jumped out a window to
OL,11,Fescape him and broke her spine.
OL,13,FHe said: "No, I didn't look that far
OL,14,Fback. Ideally, I should have started
OL,15,Fon page one and started reading about
OL,16,Fthis man, but it just doesn't work
OL,17,Flike that.
OL,19,F"His notes amounted to 273 pages in
OL,20,Flength. I arrived as his care co-
OL,21,Fordinator at page 267.
OL,26,@uD@JOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"Yes, it would have been fantastic to
OL,8,Fstart on page one and work my way
OL,9,Fthrough, but that would have taken
OL,10,Fquite some time."
OL,12,FWhen he first met Calocane ` who is
OL,13,Freferred to as VC during the inquiry `
OL,14,Fon September 15 2020, 15 days after he
OL,15,Fjoined the EIP team, he said he
OL,16,Fthought he was a "pleasant chap" and
OL,17,Fhad no concerns about his mental state.
OL,19,FHe said if Calocane was "masking" any
OL,20,Fpotential symptoms, he "did a good
OL,21,Fjob, in my opinion".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@QO]xD@ROUxD@`O]{D@YOU{D@aO]|D@
OL,26,AXOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"That's completely wrong on my part"
OL,9,FMr Carter said he felt the handover
OL,10,Fprocess, when he took over as
OL,11,FCalocane's care co-ordinator, was
OL,12,F"inadequate" and agreed that the issue
OL,13,Fof his non-compliance with taking
OL,14,Fmedication, which was mentioned in his
OL,15,Fcare plan as needing ongoing
OL,16,Fmonitoring, was not taken seriously
OL,17,Fenough.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIn a visit to Calocane on 6 November
OL,8,F2020, Mr Carter said he took one
OL,9,Fmonth's worth of medication to him,
OL,10,Fbut Calocane said he still had 10
OL,11,Ftablets left.
OL,13,F"That told you he was not taking his
OL,14,Fmedication as prescribed?," Ms
OL,15,FLangdale asked.
OL,17,F"That is correct," Mr Carter said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@[O]yD@AOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FAsked if he wanted to escalate the
OL,8,Fissue at that point, following
OL,9,Fconcerns from Dr Seedat and from
OL,10,FCalocane's mother that he was
OL,11,Frelapsing, he said: "It would appear
OL,12,Fwe didn't take it much further than
OL,13,Fthat, really."
OL,15,F"It was worse than that, you recorded
OL,16,F'no issues of concern' ` that wasn't
OL,17,Fthe case, was it?" Ms Langdale asked.
OL,26,@sD@UOUuD@NO]wD@AOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMr Carter said: "No, that's completely
OL,8,Fwrong on my part. That was my mistake
OL,9,F... obviously having 10 tablets left,
OL,10,Fthat's not compliant ... that was my
OL,11,Fmistake."
OL,13,FHe admitted it was "quite wrong" not
OL,14,Fto have asked Calocane why he had
OL,15,Ftablets left and Ms Langdale asked if
OL,16,Fhe had "got away with it".
OL,18,F"Yes, you can look at it that way...
OL,19,Fwe just didn't ask him the question,"
OL,20,FMr Carter said.
OL,26,@oD@QOUsD@IO]uD@TOUuD@`O]xD@HOUxD@YO]zD@
OL,26,AAOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe nurse also said he had not been
OL,8,Faware that Calocane had visited MI5
OL,9,Fheadquarters in London in May 2021.
OL,11,FWhen told he could have known about
OL,12,Fthe incident by reading Calocane's
OL,13,Fnotes, Mr Carter said: "Why would I
OL,14,Fhave wanted to start reading the
OL,15,Fdocuments of a client who wasn't on my
OL,16,Fcaseload?
OL,18,F"If I did that, you could say by
OL,19,Fextension I have to look through the
OL,20,Fcase notes of everyone in the office,
OL,21,Fit just doesn't make sense."
OL,26,@uD@XOUzD@AOU}D@\O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FAfter Calocane was said to have been
OL,8,F"abrupt" and "a little rude" in a
OL,9,Fphone conversation on 6 August 2021,
OL,10,FMr Carter said he was not concerned at
OL,11,Fthe time that he may be relapsing.
OL,13,FHe said: "Why, because he was rude to
OL,14,Fme? It didn't raise a red flag at that
OL,15,Fmoment in time, to be honest with you."
OL,17,FMr Carter said when he made a visit to
OL,18,FCalocane's home at the end of that
OL,19,Fmonth, he "looked very different to
OL,20,Fhow I remember him".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@HO]pD@NOUpD@\O]uD@JOUwD@gO]{D@
OL,26,AKOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"He just unnerved me"
OL,9,FHe said he felt he was on the verge of
OL,10,Fa breakdown and confirmed he was not
OL,11,Ftaking his medication.
OL,13,FMr Carter said: "He looked quite
OL,14,Fagitated ... he was quite paranoid and
OL,15,Ffelt we were working with the police.
OL,16,FI had to pull out my ID card and show
OL,17,Fhim I was a nurse.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@QOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"We needed to reassure him we worked
OL,8,Ffor the health service. I wasn't
OL,9,Fentirely convinced he was reassured by
OL,10,Fthat.
OL,12,F"He just unnerved me to see him like
OL,13,Fthat. I was glad when we exited the
OL,14,Froom.
OL,16,F"In a situation like that, you can
OL,17,Ffeel an atmosphere, you can just feel
OL,18,Fthat things are not quite right."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777669904
OL,3,CCalocane 'lied, deceived and
OL,4,Coutmanoeuvred' medical staff, nurse
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FHe said he was not in fear of physical
OL,8,Fviolence from Calocane, but felt
OL,9,Funcomfortable.
OL,11,FHe said: "I was just concerned the way
OL,12,Fhe was, I felt he hadn't been taking
OL,13,Fhis tablets and we might have to
OL,14,Finitiate something in the near future."
OL,16,FThe hearing continues.
OL,26,@sD@JOUvD@gO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/17
